Path: `salons/{salonId}` — model: `lib/features/salon/data/models/salon.dart`.

## Fields

id: string (document id)
salonId: string (equals document id; redundant for rules/queries)
name: string
phone: string
address: string
ownerUid: string (**not** ownerId — Firebase Auth uid)
ownerName: string
ownerEmail: string
currencyCode: string (default USD)
defaultPayrollPeriod: string (monthly | weekly; default monthly when missing)
isActive: boolean
createdAt: timestamp
updatedAt: timestamp

## Implemented vs Planned

**Implemented:** All fields above exist on `Salon` / `SalonRepository` writes.

**Planned:** `location` (lat/lng map), `logoUrl` — not in the current model.
